      "span_text": "Successful development of an affordable combination vaccine against diarrheal diseases for pediatric public health will rely on subsidy by international organizations, potential private sector markets among developed world travelers and the middle to upper income class of developing countries, and collaboration between the commercial manufacturer (who likely hold the patents and IP rights) and a local producer. [CITATION_1]"
